OL,4,Cpolice officer during Southport
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FA man who was caught on camera
OL,8,Fthrowing a brick at police deployed to
OL,9,Fprotect members of the public during
OL,10,Fthe Southport riots has been jailed.
OL,12,FNicholas Mullen was identified on CCTV
OL,13,Fchucking bricks towards a line of
OL,14,Fofficers in the seaside town on 30
OL,15,FJuly 2024, after riots broke out
OL,16,Ffollowing the death of three girls in
OL,17,Fa knife attack.
