OL,7,FThe 22-year-old was also captured by a
OL,8,Fpolice helicopter and on camera phone
OL,9,Ffootage taken by others engaged in
OL,10,Fdisorder.
OL,12,FDuring one particularly "shocking"
OL,13,Fmoment, Mullen struck a police
OL,14,Fconstable with a brick.
OL,16,FMullen, of Kingsley Avenue, Wigan, was
OL,17,Fsentenced to two years and eight
OL,18,Fmonths at Liverpool Crown Court on
OL,19,FThursday, 3 April, for violent
OL,20,Fdisorder and assaulting an emergency
OL,21,Fworker.
