OL,7,FMerseyside Police say 130 people have
OL,8,Fnow been sentenced for their role in
OL,9,Fthe disorder in Southport and
OL,10,FLiverpool last summer.
OL,12,FThey have been jailed for a total of
OL,13,F241 years, six months, with 191
OL,14,Farrested and 150 charged for their
OL,15,Frole in the violence inflicted on
OL,16,Fcommunities.
