OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Paula Jones said:
OL,8,F"Mullen came to a community grieving
OL,9,Fthe loss of three young girls just 24
OL,10,Fhours earlier, still reeling from the
OL,11,Fawful events of 29 July.
OL,13,F"He came here with one clear
OL,14,Fintention: to cause chaos and
OL,15,Fdestruction. His actions left rubble
OL,16,Fstrewn in our streets, and a police
OL,17,Fofficer deployed to protect our
OL,18,Fcommunity in Southport was struck with
OL,19,Fa brick.
