OL,7,F"Mullen will now have a considerable
OL,8,Ftime in prison to consider his
OL,9,Factions, and whether they furthered
OL,10,Fwhatever cause he thought he was
OL,11,Ffighting for.
OL,13,F"We know that his actions and those of
OL,14,Feveryone who took to the streets to
OL,15,Fcommit disorder that day caused
OL,16,Fnothing but fear, concern and distress
OL,17,Fto residents in the area.
